Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:03.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Viewers Sitting in Front of the Television,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:05.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the guys that appear in this anime are delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, please do not imitate what you see in this anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnAveria Sans\b1\i0\bord0\blur0.3\fad(450,0)\c&HDADADA&\fs33\pos(362.532,49)}Do not imitate{\i1\fs40}!{\i0\fs33} Or this will happen{\i1\fs40}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}僕が泣いているのは とても悔しいからです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}Boku ga naite iru no wa totemo kuyashii kara desu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)}The reason I am crying is\Nbecause I am very frustrated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.21,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}人の尊さやさしさ 踏みにじられそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.21,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Hito no toutosa yasashisa fuminijiraresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.21,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}I feel as though the nobility and\Nkindness of man is being trampled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}力を示す者達は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Chikara o shimesu mono tachi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.47,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}しなやかさを失って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.47,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Shinayakasa o ushinatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:34.47,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Those who show their strength lose their grace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}ウソまみれドロまみれ じれったい風景でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uso-mamire doro-mamire jirettai fuukei desho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:40.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Covered in dirt and lies, isn't it a vexing sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}より強くしたたかに タフな生き方をしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Yori tsuyoku shitataka ni tafu na ikikata o shimashou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's live more strongly, fiercely, and tougher
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}まっすぐ歩きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Massugu arukimasho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's walk straight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}風は向かい風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kaze wa mukai kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The wind is against us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ どけ どけ 後ろめたい奴はどけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke doke doke ushirometai yatsu wa doke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, move, move, those with\Na guilty conscience, move aside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}有象無象の町に 灯りをともせ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uzoumuzou no machi ni akari o tomose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Light up the town of riffraff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ そこ どけ 真実のお通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke soko doke shinjitsu no otouri da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, make way, truth is coming through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}正義の時代がくるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Seigi no jidai ga kuru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The era of justice will come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}希望の歌もあるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kibou no uta mo aru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}There are songs of hope too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}僕の命この世に 捧げてしまっていいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}Boku no inochi kono yo ni sasagete-shimatte ii sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)}I would happily sacrifice my life for this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:51.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is Keough Pass in north Kanto,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:53.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,a road where sharp curves\N appear one after another,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:55.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,looking as if it threads between the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:57.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Bikers who were fascinated by that pass
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:02:01.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,were competing with each other every day\Nbecause of their need for speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:05.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The legendary biker, Sadaharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:08.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The fastest man at Keough Pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:12.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Because of his genius-like riding technique,\Nno one has ever overtaken him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:18.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Countless men have challenged him\Nand been eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:20.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:25.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And these men are also about to challenge him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:27.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We'll kick his ass today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:34.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Sadaharu will show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:35.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He'll definitely come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He can smell competition, just like a wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:41.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Can we really defeat him with our skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:47.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It'll be a piece of cake!\NNo one can keep up with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:51.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah! We'll teach him that\Nhe's a big fish in a small pond!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:55.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We'll teach him who's the fastest on the Pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:58.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Is that Sadaharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:00.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's reckless!\N If he keeps up like that, he'll crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:04.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:07.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He turned that sharp corner\Nat such a high speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:08.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Is he a monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:10.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Our exit recovery is nothing compared to his!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:16.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's no good! I'm pushing it to the limit,\Nbut I still can't catch up with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:18.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We can't compete against him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:20.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We've completely lost sight of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:23.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So that's the legendary biker...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My name is Sadaharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:43.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How long has it been since I met someone\Nwho could keep up with my speed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:12.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:15.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I heard that the legendary biker retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:17.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:17.27,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\c&H5BB9B9&\3c&H8174DE&\fnAnna\shad0\bord2\fs36\pos(593.646,34)\be2\clip(m 709.25 39 l 709.25 2 474.75 -2 472.375 32 539.25 35 539.25 2 588 2 586.875 36)}Let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:21.57,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,0)\c&H5BB9B9&\3c&H8174DE&\fnAnna\shad0\bord2\fs36\pos(593.646,34)\be2}Let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:21.57,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)\fnAnna\shad0\bord0\fs22\c&H494F49&\frz0\org(204,514)\frx24\fry30\pos(145.013,418)}Cromartie High School
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.73,0:04:21.57,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnArtificeSSK\c&H5CB3FE&\3c&H181755&\shad0\blur0.6\fs42}Track and Field Competition
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:21.57,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnArtificeSSK\c&H5CB3FE&\shad0\blur10\fs42\3c&HACF5F6&}Track and Field Competition
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:26.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Runners, get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:30.33,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\move(883.671,390,-169.937,390,0,3630)}The first event - 100m race
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:35.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've been a badass since I was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:40.76,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\c&HE3E7EB&\move(759.051,113,-90.633,113,0,7050)}Akira Maeda (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:38.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but the one thing I was proud of\Nwas being a fast runner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:42.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I haven't been able to attract\N much attention since I entered Cromartie,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:44.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but finally my day in the spotlight has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:46.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I won't be beaten when it comes to running.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:49.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Absolutely no one will beat me. No one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:52.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's how I was thinking\Nup until a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:54.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's foul play!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:57.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Ready...
