Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:07.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The winner is Mechazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,A couple of people were taken\Nto the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:11.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:13.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's a motorcycle! Someone stop that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:16.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That certainly is a motorcycle,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:18.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but it used to be our friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:22.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,who wore a school uniform and was\Ntaking classes with us up until recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:27.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,so I'd feel reluctant to bluntly say\N "You're a motorcycle, aren't you," you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:30.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, let's say I concede the point\Nthat it's okay if it's a motorcycle,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:34.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but even if it becomes a rice cooker next,\Ncan you still say that that thing is our friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:38.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, don't be so edgy.\NThe next event should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:41.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The next event is the high jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,High jump...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:46.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If it's just running, he has no equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:50.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But if it's the high jump, he'll be quite helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:53.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Anyone has strengths and weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:56.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You were too naïve, Mechazawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:58.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It was your own fault for\Ngetting too carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you can, just go ahead and jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:12.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:21.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Jaka jan, Cromartie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:26.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm saying, show us all the money you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Are you listening, moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:33.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You have change, right?!\NGo ahead and jump! Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:35.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you jump, it'll jingle, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:39.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing, trying to get help?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:42.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me! No one's gonna help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:44.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's our turf around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:48.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you don't wanna get hurt,\Nshow us your money now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:49.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:51.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Stop bullying the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:00.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You wanna mess with us, dumbass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:04.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Fine! Since you're here, you jump too, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:04.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:20.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Landed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:23.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This guy's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:25.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:28.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:31.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't know how I can thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:33.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No problem. I only did what was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Or rather, I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh? You're errand-boy Tanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Looks like the police have finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:42.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I launched missiles last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:45.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,so they mistook me for a dangerous person and I got arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:48.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It took a lot of work to get released,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,so I made sure it doesn't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:53.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\pos(394.253,258)\fs20\fnAnna\c&H201C1C&}{\frz3}Th{\frz2.5}is{\frz2} veh{\frz1.5}icle {\frz1}me{\frz-1}ets {\frz-2}saf{\frz-3}ety {\frz-4}stan{\frz-4.5}da{\frz-5}rds
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:53.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm not carrying any dangerous materials today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:55.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm wearing my helmet properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:57.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The air pressure is perfect too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:00.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm properly observing the speed limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:04.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing anything that\Nviolates the law, police officers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:35.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fnAnna\fad(600,0)\c&H564555&\3c&HCDD2D6&\shad0\bord3\be2\frz348\pos(367.063,161)\frx16\fry22}All Season\N Road Safety\N Campaign\N in Effect
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:42.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,\N I didn't have a motorcycle license.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:47.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now, let's do our best\N practicing baseball again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:50.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Somehow, although it's happening little by little,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I feel we're getting close to Koshien.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:56.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Really? It's not easy for me to say this,\Nbut I think it's your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't just hang around\Nall day, you morons!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:01.20,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(358,0)\fnAnna\shad0\bord2\c&H61649C&\3c&HD5D3D3&}Hakkou Group{\r\shad0} - {\c&H57B0A9&\3c&H101374&\bord1.5\fnArial\fs26}Rainbakku
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:05.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, is this really the Cromartie\Nthat's supposed to be so terrible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:07.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Shoot! So these guys are
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:11.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the motorcycle gang Rainbakku who's been\Ninvading this neighborhood recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:13.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So they finally came to our school too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:15.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:15.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Kamiyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:18.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's no way we can\Npractice baseball like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:21.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The old me would've depended on the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:22.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but now I'm not afraid or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:23.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:27.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Frankly, compared to Mechazawa,\Nthey're nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,because, after all, he can even fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:30.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:33.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We do have a special trump card at our school!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:35.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's parked behind the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:36.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:38.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You stay here, Maeda, for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:43.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's been stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:55.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\i1}Into the sky of hope
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:03.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\i1}You put all your strength and fighting spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:07.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\i1}Can you do it? I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:11.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\i1}Your heart is always\N geared up for a critical battle
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:15.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\i1}You're world-famous brave men
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:21.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\i1}Even if life's easy here, you call it Cro, Cro
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:35.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\i1}Ah, Cromartie is our alma mater
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:44.97,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\alpha130\fs24\fnNeon\bord0\c&H4E1728&\blur0.5\pos(346.671,139)}Next\N\N\N\NEpisode
