Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:49.97,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\shad0\fs36\bord2.2\blur0.5\pos(385.19,390)\c&HFCFCFE&}Mechazawa, protect world peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:36.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:38.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sakigake!! Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:40.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's time for Takashi Kamiyama's\None point living course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:42.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,"Sakigake" can be taken care of with just\None character if written as kanji,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:44.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,while it requires four letters if written in hiragana.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Go, Mechazawa Wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mechazawa Wing?
